Domain intelligence scanner - scan URLs and export results.

Usage: domain_status <COMMAND>

Commands:
  scan    Scan URLs and store results in SQLite database
  export  Export data from SQLite database to various formats
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
